------------------------------------------------------
|0 |EXCHANGE IN REMOTE  |             |100      |432 |
|1 | EXCHANGE OUT REMOTE|             |100      |423 |
|2 |  TABLE SCAN        |t3(idx_e1_e2)|100      |423 |
======================================================

